---
title: Mediterranean Roasted Eggplant Fusilli with Feta
description: Our meat-free marvels make it easy (and delicious) to mix up your cooking routine whenever you like. Add layers of flavour to
fusilli with an array of rainbow veggies roasted in Mediterranean-inspired seasonings. Paired with a rich cherry tomato sauce
and creamy feta, your finished dish will be transformed into a taste sensation.

